tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE survey_responses (
  response_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  survey_id INT,
  respondent_id INT,
  question_id INT,
  answer_text TEXT,
  answer_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE survey_responses (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  question_id INT,
  user_id INT,
  response VARCHAR(255),
  response_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE survey_summary (
  question_id INT,
  total_responses INT,
  average_response_length FLOAT,
  max_response_length INT,
  min_response_length INT
);

CREATE TABLE survey_responses (
    response_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    survey_id INT,
    question_id INT,
    response_text TEXT,
    response_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE survey_results (
    result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    survey_id INT,
    participant_id INT,
    question_id INT,
    response_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE survey_results (
  result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  response_id INT,
  question_id INT,
  user_id INT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  score INT
);
